Yes, we added an optional Hash in recent updates.    

CertIndirectReference ::= SEQUENCE {
         location CertLocation,
         certHash [0] IMPLICIT CertHash OPTIONAL
      }

We solved this using a `CertReference` structure:

~~~
CertReference ::= CHOICE {
      direct Certificate,
      indirect [0] IMPLICIT CertIndirectReference
   }

CertIndirectReference ::= SEQUENCE {
         location CertLocation,
         certHash [0] IMPLICIT CertHash OPTIONAL
      }
~~~

So a direct certificate can be included if needed.

